              <title>Track OER project: tracking Open Educational Resources</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6196</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6196</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>"New JISC project TRACK OER: OER in the wild can get lost. We will add the tracer to find where they go for attribution, research and remix." from <a title="Patrick McAndrew, 8 March 2012, on Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/openpad/status/177821209684226048">@openpad</a>.</p>
<p>This is the blog for a HEA/JISC-funded project in the Open Educational Resource (OER) rapid innovation programme. The project will run from 1 April to 19 October 2012 at The Open University.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>]]></description>
