<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Broadband, platforms, speed of uptake, ease of finding quality.</div>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->2: Markey conditions</div>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Prices down, supply up, hardware, tools &ndash; cloud, open source, kids as experts, NGOs that can support</div>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->3: Choice for use of technology &ndash; how useful?</div>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Simple, easy, reliable, OER adds free and ease of adaptation</div>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->4: Cultural fit</div>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->No disrespect of threat</div>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->5: Add value?</div>
<div id="_mcePaste" style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Creates new access &ndash; OER opens locked boxes.</div>
