<p>Melissa described the work on OpenSpires supported by the JISC/HEA programme &ndash; this has built on approach to podcasting, using open source platforms and sharing content but with more specific attention paid to the openness and suitable licensing for reuse. In particular using creative commons.</p>]]></description>
