              <title>Scenario: Tools and methods to support a learner of spanish</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/1833</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/1833</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<!--StartFragment--><p class="MsoNormal">I am a learner of Spanish. I want to be able to findlearning patterns and tools to help me with different aspects of my learning. Iwant a way to connect with other learners at the same level. I want to havedifferent structured suggestions for sessions with study buddies. I want amechanism to check my understanding of something with a peer. I want resourcesand tools related to specific aspects of my learning. I want a means ofaggregating my learning space<span>  </span>- soI can aggregate my resources and so that I can see my progress/development. Iwant different aspects of ‘good’ pedagogy in relation to language learning tobe made explicit and usable for me but not in a patronising way. </p><p class="MsoNormal">System has a bank of designs and patterns that aremeta-tagged with key words that can be presented to the learner depending onwhat they enter in terms of what they want. But also the learner can start tobecome part of a shared community so that they can discuss and share withothers.</p><p class="MsoNormal">Components: Designs/patterns, resources, tools, community</p><p class="MsoNormal">Someone demonstrate the power of visualisation</p><!--EndFragment-->]]></description>
